HEADWORD: Dispatchful
<hw>Dis*patch"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Bent on haste;
intent on speedy execution of business or any task; indicating haste;
quick; <as>as, <ex>dispatchful</ex> looks</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

